content: I cannot have personal opinions or tastes. however, in terms of showcasing tyler, the creator's range the most, it would be hard to pinpoint one specific collaboration, as they all offer unique and different styles that showcase his versatility as an artist. however, collaborations such as "igor's theme" featuring lil uzi vert and solange, "earfquake" featuring playboi carti, and "911/mr. lonely" featuring frank ocean display tyler's ability to experiment with different sounds and incorporate them into his own unique style.
